These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, may, november
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, motorbike, helicopter
1. the person driving the motorbike is in the middle##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Birthday   | july | may | november   |
| Transport      | skateboard    | motorbike  | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, comedy, epic
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, coral, lilac
1. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person who likes coral is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes coral is the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Movie-Genre      | comedy | animation     | epic      |
| Color   | coral | lavender | lilac |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, board-games, baking
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, chestnut, red
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who likes red##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Hobby   | fishing | baking  | board-games       |
| Color       | lavender     | chestnut | red |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, trike, train
The people have 3 different jobs:  pilot, analyst, scientist
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the scientist##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the pilot##1
3. the scientist is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Transport    | train    | trike     | jet-ski |
| Job   | scientist | pilot | analyst     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, october, september
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, salsa, r&b
1. the fan of salsa is the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Birthday         | october | june     | september |
| Music-Genre   | r&b        | ambient | salsa    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, december, february
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, dog, goldfish
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Birthday        | february | august      | december  |
| Pet   | rabbit       | dog | goldfish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, may, january
3 different games are played: snooker, poker, go
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is the person playing poker##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Birthday   | january      | march     | may    |
| Game           | snooker | go | poker |

