.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: turquise, pink, purple
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, poppy, balloon-flower
1. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
2. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
3. the person who likes pink is the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Color    | purple | turquise | pink      |
| Flower   | zinnia     | balloon-flower | poppy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, tulip, marigold
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, ritmeester, montecristo
1. the fonseca-smoker is the person who growstulip##1
2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Flower   | marigold | tulip | poppy  |
| Cigar     | montecristo     | fonseca      | ritmeester |

