.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
3 different games are played: snooker, domino, canasta
City: boston, colone, paris
1. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person playing domino##1
2. the person traveling to paris is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Game      | snooker   | domino    | canasta    |
| City   | colone | boston | paris |

