.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-13::.
City: new-york, prague, boston
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, daisy, zinnia
1. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
2. the person traveling to boston is in the middle##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| City   | new-york     | boston   | prague     |
| Flower    | zinnia | daisy | amaryllis |

