.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-14::.
3 different games are played: snooker, canasta, go
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, march, october
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person playing go##1
2. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| Game   | snooker    | go | canasta |
| Birthday   | october | december     | march        |

