.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, lily, amaryllis
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, light-blue, aquamarine
1. the person who growslily is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who growslily##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Flower      | sunflower  | amaryllis | lily  |
| Color   | light-blue | aquamarine   | yellow |

