2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
3. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |   3    |
| Flower   | zinnia | balloon-flower | aconite    |
| Nationality        | colombian    | polish | russian |

