.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  police-officer, dressmaker, mechanic
3 different games are played: chess, go, bridge
1. the person playing go is in the middle##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the left of the police-officer##1
3. the dressmaker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Job    | mechanic | police-officer       | dressmaker  |
| Game   | bridge  | go | chess |

 